Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:28.71,OP-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}現実を今に映す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.80,0:01:34.15,OP-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}幾つもの空を描いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:38.83,OP-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}ここはきっと儚い心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:41.56,OP-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.59,0:01:45.63,OP-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}夢で高く飛んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:52.01,OP-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}身体はどんな不安纏っても振り払ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:56.51,OP-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}守る小さな思い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:58.70,OP-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}広がり出して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:00.87,OP-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}気付く弱い私
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:07.56,OP-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}君が居れば暗い世界強く居れた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:13.25,OP-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}長い夢見る心は そう永遠で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:17.36,OP-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:23.41,OP-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}I give you everything i have
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:11.75,OP-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}对怯懦的过去我已认命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:18.12,OP-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}就让自己懵懂无知下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:21.96,OP-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}曾经那个胆小无助的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:28.71,OP-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}将现实映在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.80,0:01:34.15,OP-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}想象过无数的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:38.83,OP-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}现在一定以虚幻无常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:41.56,OP-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}心中目标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.59,0:01:45.63,OP-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}在梦里高高飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:52.01,OP-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}即使被缠上再多的不安 也能抖落掸去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:56.51,OP-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}想要守护的小小情感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:58.70,OP-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}渐渐变得强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:00.87,OP-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}意识到自己的弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:07.56,OP-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}只要有你在即使世界一片黑暗也能坚强生存
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:13.25,OP-ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,400)}{\blur8}一直想梦想成真的心 永远等待着
